{"tid":2130542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大三罷】涉藏噴漆《堵路指南》手冊等 19歲男生准自簽守行為","createTime":"2020-07-29T09:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T09:50:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b88d13be7a1df8c4ffc7d674276d0a8b2148243","tid":2130542,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:15:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7523&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6TC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=6f82f19e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7523</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院５樓1庭<br />\n#嚴舜儀主任裁判官 #答辯<br />\n#1111旺角<br />\n👤陳(19)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有物品意圖損壞財產  <br />\n<br />\n案件背景:<br />\n去年 11 月 11 日發起「三罷」行動，其中在旺角爆發警民衝突，被告被控同日在旺角亞皆老街與彌敦道一帶管有物品意圖損壞財產，即保管兩支黑色噴漆。。//（立場新聞撰寫）<br />\n<br />\n🎉🎉撤回控罪🎉🎉<br />\n被告簽保守行為🎊 罰款$2000，24個月內不得涉及所有刑事個案。"},{"pid":"0239ee6ab471dd49e856056091e84e4567cb122a","tid":2130542,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"但有位手足要坐18個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e60de0b2f1301e212d77abd06ef90a19e37446","tid":2130542,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"拎住本龍虎豹唔知條臭閪又UP得出D咩花款"},{"pid":"1b7cff9406c99559fd948bb6b140934f07f8d7b1","tid":2130542,"uid":46906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0239ee6ab471dd49e856056091e84e4567cb122a","tid":2130542,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"但有位手足要坐18個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"依家玩人治同撞手神無分別"},{"pid":"021eba7fb4e15b499572069693bb22109233baeb","tid":2130542,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:19:04.000Z","msg":"六角匙 食用油 索帶 噴漆<br 